FW Final Version Red Rock AgreementOriginal Message From mailto Sent Friday June AM To Cammarano Joseph A Subject Final Version Red Rock Agreement Joe Heres the final version for your approval and execution As we discussed if possible we need you to execute and return via facsimile a signed copy as soon as possible this morning You are the last contract to get signed here and we are at the deadline to authorize GE to proceed on the turbine production schedule today Also look for a facsimile from me that has the form Transportation Agreement attached Youll need to sign that and return it along with the Privileged and Confidential Agreement I know we were diametrically opposed on a couple of issues here but I genuinely appreciate your professionalism and commitment to see this negotiation through to a successful conclusion Thank you Regards Jeff PPLredrockagreementfinalversiondoc PPLredrockagreementfinalversiondoc
